title: Whats the weather this week in london

messages.content: Whats the weather this week in london

Based on the provided search results, here is a summary of the weather forecast for London this week:

- **Today (Friday)**: Expect rain showers in the early part of the day transitioning to overcast skies later. The high temperature will be around 48°F with East winds between 5 to 10 mph [1].
  
- **General Week Outlook**: The Met Office reports a 7-day forecast indicating chances of rain and overcast conditions throughout the week, with temperatures ranging approximately between 45°F (7°C) and 50°F (10°C). There may be weather warnings in effect that are worth monitoring [2].

For more detailed hourly forecasts or air quality information, you can refer to AccuWeather's sources [3] and [5], though specific daily details beyond today are not provided. If needed, a broader 14-day forecast is available on timeanddate.com [4]. 

Stay prepared for rain and keep an eye out for any weather warnings as advised by the Met Office.
